fun a bisl broyne vaser mit eyn shtikl broyt.

220
00:10:26,566 --> 00:10:29,516
un tsvelf a zeyger fleg men oysrufn da-

221
00:10:29,516 --> 00:10:32,516
frishtik iz geendikt, yetst vet ir esn mitog.

222
00:10:32,516 --> 00:10:37,566
der mitog iz bashtanen fun a bisl reyne, vareme vaser mit eyn shtikl broyt.

223
00:10:37,416 --> 00:10:38,616
di zelbe?

224
00:10:38,466 --> 00:10:41,066
yo. in etlekhe teg

225
00:10:41,066 --> 00:10:44,066
oyb emetser hot bakumen a shtikl broyt iz er geven a gliklekher.

226
00:10:44,416 --> 00:10:46,916
nor mir tsufelik hot opgeglikt

227
00:10:46,916 --> 00:10:49,140
farn araynfaln in plen

228
00:10:49,216 --> 00:10:55,566
hot men tseteylt ales vos iz geven, hob ikh gekhapt nor broyt. andere hobn gekhapt andere zakhn. ikh hob gekhapt nor tsvey lebelekh broyt.

229
00:10:55,766 --> 00:11:01,716
un dos hot mir geholfn oystsuhaltn di shlekhte tsayt bizn antloyfn fun lager.

230
00:11:01,716 --> 00:11:03,377
mit tsvey leblekh broyt.

231
00:11:03,452 --> 00:11:05,332
dos iz geven tayerer vi gold!

232
00:11:07,316 --> 00:11:11,916
dos heyst, dos heyst bay, z- der der lebn in lager iz geven zeyer a shlekhter, on esn,

233
00:11:12,766 --> 00:11:19,516
un vaser iz geven, fir kranen iz geven vaser in gantsn tsu toyznt-, nit keyn vaser, nit keyn esn, gornit geven.

234
00:11:20,816 --> 00:11:23,151
du host gearbet dortn in di lager?

235
00:11:22,412 --> 00:11:25,766
NO NO, s'iz di ershte teg fun der milkhome geven.

236
00:11:25,766 --> 00:11:26,896
dos iz glaykh di ershte teg...

237
00:11:25,950 --> 00:11:27,827
vi lang host geven in di lager?

238
00:11:27,347 --> 00:11:27,823
oh.

239
00:11:27,823 --> 00:11:29,669
in lager bin ikh geven tsen teg.

240
00:11:29,977 --> 00:11:32,977
un me hot undz aroysgefirt oyf arbet,

241
00:11:34,427 --> 00:11:37,727
ontsulodn holts, kletser. groyse kletser onlodn.

242
00:11:37,727 --> 00:11:39,977
akhtsn mentshn hobn gekayklt a klots.

243
00:11:40,827 --> 00:11:46,877
un mir zaynen gekumen oyfn ban-stantsye, un me hot gekayklt di kletser. m'hot ongelodevet vagones holts, kletser,

244
00:11:47,127 --> 00:11:50,177
tsu firn farrikhtn a brik in Ostrolenko.

245
00:11:51,027 --> 00:11:57,277
ikh hob gehert vi di poylishe ban-arbeter hobn geredt tsvishn zikh poylish, un azoy vi ikh hob farshtanen

246
00:11:57,777 --> 00:12:01,327
hob ikh farshtanen az zey forn in Ostrolenko firn di holts.

247
00:12:01,477 --> 00:12:04,127
hob ikh gezogt tsu maynem a khaver, a Vilner,

248
00:12:04,727 --> 00:12:05,977
"lomir antloyfn,

249
00:12:06,077 --> 00:12:08,777
anit vet men shtarbn fun hunger. s'iz nito keyn oysveg".

250
00:12:09,277 --> 00:12:11,177
zogt er, "gut, lomir pruvn".

251
00:12:11,877 --> 00:12:14,027
az me hot gelo- -endikt

252
00:12:14,027 --> 00:12:18,627
onlodn di holts iz shoyn gevorn halb tunkl, azoy farnakht.

253
00:12:18,627 --> 00:12:21,177
zey hobn arayngeshprungen in a farlozene hayzke

254
00:12:21,477 --> 00:12:22,777
un mir hobn zikh bahaltn.

255
00:12:23,827 --> 00:12:25,427
vu host gehaltn?

256
00:12:25,027 --> 00:12:26,923
oyfn, oyfn ban-stantsye

257
00:12:26,923 --> 00:12:29,177
in a farlozene hayzke, mir hobn zikh bahaltn zikh.

258
00:12:29,427 --> 00:12:32,477
un ikh hob gehert az zey hobn gezogt az tsvelf a zeyger fort op der ban.

259
00:12:32,927 --> 00:12:33,927
tsvelf bay nakht.

260
00:12:34,827 --> 00:12:36,477
nu, mir hobn gevart,

261
00:12:38,227 --> 00:12:40,227
keyn zeyger hob ikh nit gehat.

262
00:12:40,377 --> 00:12:44,627
nor kh'hob gezen vi di ban-arbeter kontrolirn di reder,

263
00:12:45,127 --> 00:12:47,977
hob ikh farshtanen az zey gey- azoy vi kh'hob gearbet oyfn ban,

264
00:12:47,977 --> 00:12:51,277
kh'hob gehat di gantse tsayt ba- batsiung mit di ban-arb-, kh'hob gevust di ale zakhn.

265
00:12:51,527 --> 00:12:53,777
hob ikh farshtanen az zey geyen bald opforn.

266
00:12:54,927 --> 00:13:00,777
mir hobn zikh arayngekhapt zikh in a leydike budke fun a vagon. s'iz do di budkes, di tormozne budkes heyst dos.

267
00:13:00,927 --> 00:13:03,427
kh'hob alts gekent, fun banen, zakhn, hob ikh alts gekent.

268
00:13:03,427 --> 00:13:08,077
do- arayngekhapt in der tormozne budke, mir zaynen gelegn bahaltn. kh'hob aropgelozt zikh oyf der erd, bin ikh bahaltn.

269
00:13:08,377 --> 00:13:10,227
tsum glik hot men undz nit gefunen,

270
00:13:10,527 --> 00:13:13,527
un der ban iz opgeforn nokh Ostrolenko.

271
00:13:14,577 --> 00:13:16,677
mir zaynen gekumen bay Ostrolenko,

272
00:13:16,677 --> 00:13:20,577
hob ikh gezogt tsu mayn khaver, "lomir aropshpringen, veln mir zikh ophaltn, kenen mir a mol zukhn..."

273
00:13:20,577 --> 00:13:24,327
hot der ban ongehoybn ts-, pamelekh tsu geyn, zaynen mir aropgeshprungen beyde.

274
00:13:24,727 --> 00:13:28,827
mir zaynen aropgeshprungen, ober vi geyt men ariber dem taykh? dort iz a groyser taykh

275
00:13:28,827 --> 00:13:33,127
un der brik iz geven tseruinirt. zey hobn gefirt di holts farrikhtn dem brik.

276
00:13:34,027 --> 00:13:35,427
zaynen mir gegangen

277
00:13:35,777 --> 00:13:39,627
noent tsum breg fun vaser un m'hot getrofn a kleyne shifele.

278
00:13:40,927 --> 00:13:41,986
geven tsu...

279
00:13:41,369 --> 00:13:42,409
vi kleyn?

280
00:13:42,727 --> 00:13:46,536
far a fish, a fisher-shifele vos me fort oyf FISHING.

281
00:13:43,300 --> 00:13:44,095
vi groys?

282
00:13:47,377 --> 00:13:55,527
zaynen mir ara- arayn in f- ober vi nemt, di fi- di shifl iz geven tsugebundn mit a, mit a hil- mit a dos, mit a, mit a shtrik.

283
00:13:55,677 --> 00:13:59,277
m'hot dokh gornit gehat bay zikh. hot men genumen tsvey shteyner, ibergeklapt dem shtrik.

284
00:13:59,527 --> 00:14:01,827
un mit di hent hot men zikh aribergeshift oyfn tsveytn zayt.

285
00:14:02,227 --> 00:14:09,627
mir zaynen gekumen oyfn tsveytn zayt iz azoy. fun dem zayt zaynen geven di daytshn, oyfn tsveytn zayt zaynen geven di rusn, der taykh iz geven der ibergang.

286
00:14:09,977 --> 00:14:11,427
hobn undz di rusn farhaltn.

287
00:14:12,527 --> 00:14:20,977
di rusn farhaltn, hobn zey mir gefre- gefregt vos tuen mir, vos makhn mir. hobn mir gezogt, zest dokh, mir zaynen, poylishe zakhn, mir zaynen antlofn fun krigs-gefangenshaft-lager.

288
00:14:22,077 --> 00:14:24,827
un er hot gezen take rikhtik vi mir zeen oys,

289
00:14:25,127 --> 00:14:28,477
oysgehungert, oysgematert un un di poylishe zakhn.

290
00:14:28,477 --> 00:14:30,377
zogt er, geyt aheym.

291
00:14:30,827 --> 00:14:31,977
bafrayt!

292
00:14:32,781 --> 00:14:33,489
tsu Vilne.

293
00:14:33,527 --> 00:14:35,927
der zelner. der rusisher zelner hot undz bafrayt.

294
00:14:36,327 --> 00:14:40,577
n-, zaynen mir gegangen vayter, ober damolst bin ikh shoyn gegangen

295
00:14:40,677 --> 00:14:42,127
biz Lomzhe

296
00:14:42,127 --> 00:14:44,327
bin ikh dergangen. mir zaynen beyde dergangen tsu fus.

297
00:14:44,627 --> 00:14:46,477
s'hot gedoyert etlekhe teg.

298
00:14:46,477 --> 00:14:50,677
geshpayzt hobn mir zikh mit roye kartofl.

299
00:14:50,777 --> 00:14:51,884
mir flegn arop-...

300
00:14:51,301 --> 00:14:52,660
vos host geesn?

301
00:14:52,827 --> 00:14:54,826
ot dos zog ikh, dos zog ikh vos kh'hob gegesn.

302
00:14:52,863 --> 00:14:53,545
in dem tsayt?

303
00:14:54,977 --> 00:14:56,177
roye kartofl.

304
00:14:56,177 --> 00:14:58,577
un mir hobn oykh gegesn beryoze,

305
00:14:58,577 --> 00:15:00,577
&lt;kore f-&gt; beryoze fun di boymer.

306
00:15:00,577 --> 00:15:04,077
yunge beryozke. dos iz zeyer gezunt un zis. me ken es fardayen.

307
00:15:04,227 --> 00:15:07,677
un tsu-, a mol hobn mir getrofn tsuker-burikes oyf di felder.

308
00:15:07,777 --> 00:15:09,877
dos hobn mir zikh bashpayzt zikh.

309
00:15:09,877 --> 00:15:13,527
mir zaynen ongekumen in Lomzhe ober keyn koyekh hobn mir nit gehat mer tsu geyn.

310
00:15:13,827 --> 00:15:18,027
hobn mir oyfgezukht a a a balegole, a mentsh mit a ferd

311
00:15:18,027 --> 00:15:21,527
un gebetn er zol undz firn in Byalistok.

312
00:15:21,527 --> 00:15:25,577
vayle in Lomzhe iz geven tseshtert der ban, nit geven keyn bavegung fun di banen.

313
00:15:25,577 --> 00:15:27,027
m'hot &lt;im&gt; bombardirt.

314
00:15:28,327 --> 00:15:31,577
gut, hobn mir im batsolt, me hot undz gefirt keyn Byalistok.

315
00:15:31,327 --> 00:15:33,655
mit vos hot, hostu im batsolt?

316
00:15:32,777 --> 00:15:34,281
kh'hob gehat gelt bay zikh.

317
00:15:34,163 --> 00:15:34,513
ah!

318
00:15:34,281 --> 00:15:36,177
farn araynfaln in plen

319
00:15:36,227 --> 00:15:41,227
hot der general tseteylt, alemen gegebn, ikh gedenk nit, toyznt zlotes, tsi toyznt finf hundert zlotes.

320
00:15:41,227 --> 00:15:43,527
hot er, un aleyn hot er zikh dershosn, der general.

321
00:15:43,777 --> 00:15:46,577
er hot gezogt, farn koved fun Poyln

322
00:15:47,377 --> 00:15:48,977
un di foter-land

323
00:15:48,977 --> 00:15:50,577
gey ikh nit in plen.

324
00:15:50,889 --> 00:15:53,877
hot alemen tseteylt di gelt, di broyt vos er hot gehat,

325
00:15:54,127 --> 00:15:55,827
un aleyn hot er zikh dershosn zikh.

326
00:15:57,977 --> 00:16:01,827
kumendik in Byalistok iz geven azoy far tog.

327
00:16:02,127 --> 00:16:05,227
vu geyt men? in di poylishe zakhn, me vet dokh undz arestirn.

328
00:16:05,327 --> 00:16:07,377
me tor dokh nit arumgeyn in di poylishe zakhn.

329
00:16:07,427 --> 00:16:10,077
zaynen mir avek in a park, in a vinkl fun park,

330
00:16:10,077 --> 00:16:12,677
zikh bahaltn zikh un zikh gezetst oyf a benkl.

331
00:16:14,127 --> 00:16:16,727
mir zaynen fun midkeyt zaynen mir ayngeshlofn.

332
00:16:17,177 --> 00:16:18,472
mit di zelbe kleyder?

333
00:16:18,427 --> 00:16:20,427
altsdi- un do iz di geshikhte, di historye.

334
00:16:20,427 --> 00:16:21,368
di zelbe kleyder.

335
00:16:21,368 --> 00:16:23,027
f- mir zaynen ayngeshlofn.

336
00:16:23,227 --> 00:16:25,277
mir hobn zikh oyfgekhapt un s'iz geven

337
00:16:25,277 --> 00:16:29,427
mistome tsen a zeyger, vayle mir hobn gezen froyen mit kinder geyen shpatsirn in park.

338
00:16:29,777 --> 00:16:33,577
un zey hobn derzen poylishe krigs-gefangene, zaynen zey tsugelofn fregn,

339
00:16:33,577 --> 00:16:36,577
"efsher hostu gezen mayn tatn, efsher hostu gezen mayn man, efsher..."

340
00:16:37,077 --> 00:16:43,627
nu, kh'hob zey alemen geentfert di zelbe e- s'iz geven a groyse tsetuml, un s'iz geven a groyse bombardirung, me hot shtark bombardirt, yo, du kenst zen.

341
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:46,177
mir zaynen koym antlofn mitn lebn,

342
00:16:47,277 --> 00:16:48,777
ober vos tut men vayter?

343
00:16:49,377 --> 00:16:52,427
iz tsugekumen a, tsugekumen tsu undz a yidishe froy un gezogt,

344
00:16:52,577 --> 00:16:54,477
"kumt mit mir tsu mir in shtub".

345
00:16:54,677 --> 00:16:55,777
in Byalistok.

346
00:16:57,477 --> 00:16:59,477
mir zaynen avek tsu ir in shtub.

347
00:16:59,477 --> 00:17:02,427
un zi hot undz gegebn zikh optsuvashn.

348
00:17:02,427 --> 00:17:05,527
oprazirn zikh. mir zaynen geven nit razirt.

349
00:17:05,727 --> 00:17:07,927
hot zi gefregt tsi mir esn

350
00:17:07,927 --> 00:17:09,377
nit keyn koshere.

351
00:17:09,377 --> 00:17:11,977
nu, mir hobn gehat an oysveg? mir hobn gegesn vos me hot undz gegebn.

352
00:17:12,277 --> 00:17:16,977
der iker, der esn, mir hobn mir hobn zikh gut ongegesn ober mir hobn es nit getort ton,

353
00:17:16,977 --> 00:17:20,927
vayl nokh azoy fil tsayt hungern tor men nit esn mit eyn mol tsu der zet.

354
00:17:20,977 --> 00:17:22,677
hobn mir gebrokhn.

355
00:17:23,427 --> 00:17:24,727
tsurik.

356
00:17:25,177 --> 00:17:27,077
arayn in &lt;vane m-&gt;

357
00:17:27,077 --> 00:17:31,127
zi hot undz, zi hot zeyer nebekh gelitn fun undz. mir hobn ge- farmakht umetum.

358
00:17:32,077 --> 00:17:33,827
zogt zi, "rut zikh op".

359
00:17:33,827 --> 00:17:37,477
s'iz gekumen fir a zeyger zogt zi, "mayn man darf kumen fun der arbet

360
00:17:38,177 --> 00:17:41,627
un ikh ken aykh nit haltn vayl mayn man iz a parteyner.

361
00:17:41,627 --> 00:17:43,627
er arbet in komunistisher partey".

362
00:17:44,427 --> 00:17:45,227
farfaln.

363
00:17:45,577 --> 00:17:50,527
nor zi hot zikh dervust un gezogt az tsvelf a zeyger bay nakht geyt op a ban nokh Vilne.

364
00:17:52,527 --> 00:17:54,664
mir zaynen avek vayter in park. vu geyt men?

365
00:17:54,664 --> 00:17:58,277
s'iz nito vos zi ken... er lozt undz nit arayn. ale hobn moyre gehat far di rusishe.

366
00:17:58,727 --> 00:18:02,977
zaynen mir avek in park un gevart. yeder sh-, yeder minut iz geven bay undz a yor.

367
00:18:03,677 --> 00:18:08,477
az mir hobn derlebt di tsayt, s'iz gekumen halb tsvelf zaynen mir avek, avek oyfn vokzal.

368
00:18:09,527 --> 00:18:13,831
di shprakh hobn mir gekent, hobn mir zikh dervust zikh velkhe ban es geyt oyf Vilne.

369
00:18:13,831 --> 00:18:16,400
mir zaynen arayn in ban un gezetst zikh, azoy vi ale zitsn.

370
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,677
oyfn veg

371
00:18:20,677 --> 00:18:23,827
hobn mir zikh tsuzamen geredt mit tsvey rusishe yidn.

372
00:18:23,827 --> 00:18:26,127
neyn, ne-, vart. s'iz geven shpeter iz es geven.

373
00:18:26,227 --> 00:18:29,477
zaynen mir gezesn ba- mir zaynen geforn, mir zaynen gekumen biz Grodne.

374
00:18:29,827 --> 00:18:32,277
in Grodne zaynen arayn roytarmeyer,

375
00:18:32,527 --> 00:18:33,577
un geshrien,

376
00:18:33,600 --> 00:18:36,077
"poylishe krigs-gefangene aroys!"

377
00:18:36,577 --> 00:18:39,327
mir zaynen geven in mundirn, me hot keyn breyre nit gehat.

378
00:18:39,777 --> 00:18:45,427
bin ikh aroysgelofn fun tsveytn, ikh bin geven bakant mit di vagones, dos hot gev- dos hot mir a bisl geholfn.

379
00:18:46,077 --> 00:18:53,427
bin ikh aroys fun tsveytn zayt, zikh geshtelt zikh fun di fintstern zayt fun vokzal. veyst dokh der vokzal geyt eyn zayt baloykhtn un fun tsveytn zayt iz tunkl.

380
00:18:54,077 --> 00:18:55,227
un hob ge-

381
00:18:55,577 --> 00:18:59,677
avekgeleygt zikh bay der erd un gevart, az der ban vet opgeyn vel ikh zikh aroyfkhapn.

382
00:18:59,677 --> 00:19:01,827
mayn khaver iz arayn in a,

383
00:19:01,827 --> 00:19:02,977
in a TOILET

384
00:19:03,177 --> 00:19:04,177
zikh bahaltn.

385
00:19:05,227 --> 00:19:07,727
ikh bin aroyf ts- der ban hot ongehoybn tsu rirn.

386
00:19:07,777 --> 00:19:10,127
hob ikh zikh gekhapt farn hentl un aroyf tsurik.

387
00:19:10,527 --> 00:19:13,677
un avekgezetst zikh lebn di zelbe yidn vos hobn gezesn frier.

388
00:19:14,627 --> 00:19:18,027
un kh'hob gezukht mayn khaver, tsum badoyern, im hot men aropgenumen.

389
00:19:18,427 --> 00:19:24,400
un er iz umgekumen in rusishn plen iz er umgekumen. in rusishn gefangenshaft iz er umgekumen.

390
00:19:24,777 --> 00:19:30,577
az mir zaynen geforn vayter, hob ikh gezen di shpil fun Grodne, hob ikh getrakht, in Vilne ken ikh shoyn nit araynforn.

391
00:19:30,577 --> 00:19:32,427
vayle me vet dokh mir vider arestirn.

392
00:19:32,627 --> 00:19:34,559
hob ikh zikh opgeredt mit di tsvey yidn,

393
00:19:34,559 --> 00:19:37,127
gegebn mayn adres fun Vilne,

394
00:19:37,227 --> 00:19:40,827
un gebetn zey zoln onzogn mayn froy az ikh leb,

395
00:19:41,027 --> 00:19:45,277
un ikh gefin zikh in di un in di shtetl. vayle ikh hob di gegnt zeyer gut gekent.

396
00:19:45,427 --> 00:19:46,912
Landverove hot es geheysn.

397
00:19:46,912 --> 00:19:49,227
dos iz finf un tsvantsik kilometer far Vilne.

398
00:19:50,227 --> 00:19:51,527
un ikh bin,

399
00:19:51,527 --> 00:19:54,377
s'iz gekumen in Landverove, hot zikh geshtelt, bin ikh aropgelofn

400
00:19:54,396 --> 00:19:55,477
fun ban.

401
00:19:55,477 --> 00:19:57,427
ober vu geyt men vayter?

402
00:19:57,427 --> 00:19:59,977
bin ikh avek in a shule, in a sinagoge.

403
00:20:00,477 --> 00:20:03,220
nu, kh'hob geredt dem rov, kh'hob im dertseylt az s-

404
00:20:02,720 --> 00:20:03,630
in in Vilne?

405
00:20:03,677 --> 00:20:06,292
NO, NO, nit in Vil-, NO, tsu Vilne iz nokh vayt.

406
00:20:03,992 --> 00:20:04,370
NO.

407
00:20:04,370 --> 00:20:05,204
nisht in Vilne?

408
00:20:05,649 --> 00:20:06,740
vi hot dos geven?

409
00:20:06,750 --> 00:20:11,277
